            <p>
             Elaine Leong and Moi Liu—both MBA 19s and roommates at Haas—landed a sit-down interview during winter break with Christine Lam, CEO of Citi China, to talk about the keys to her successful finance career. Leong wasn’t going into Citi cold; she’d worked as a management associate at Citi in Malaysia before applying to Haas. At
