            </div>
            <p>
             In honor of Black History Month, we’re running a series of profiles and Q&amp;As with members of the African-American community at Haas. Follow the series throughout February. Haas lecturer Jennifer R. Cohen is gearing up to launch a course called “Equitable and Inclusive Leadership,” this summer. The elective is open to both Evening &amp; Weekend and
