            <h3>
             Poets &amp; Quants
            </h3>
            <span class="headdate">
             Feb 21
            </span>
            <span class="excrpt">
             <p>
              Katie Rentz, MBA 20, is named among 10 remarkable women to watch by Poets &amp; Quants. Rentz was a Surface Warfare Officer with the U.S. Navy, deployed to Iraq. Now an aspiring project manager, Rentz is focused on breaking into the tech sector.
             </p>
