            <h3>
             San Francisco Chronicle (Datebook)
            </h3>
            <span class="headdate">
             Mar 1
            </span>
            <span class="excrpt">
             <p>
              Komal Shah, MBA 97, and her husband Gaurav Garg were named last year by ARTnews magazine as among the world’s top 200 art collectors. Shah serves on the board of trustees of the San Francisco Museum of Modern Art and the Tate Americas Foundation, among others. She is also a founding board member for the Center for Equity, Gender, and Leadership (EGAL) at Haas.
             </p>
